&lt;p&gt;Without us, crypto is just a whitepaper. We make it real. Coinbase Institutional builds cutting-edge platforms that allow thousands of the world’s largest financial institutions to trade, custody, and participate in the global cryptoeconomy. From launching industry &quot;firsts&quot; to scaling secure infrastructure for hundreds of digital assets, we provide the trusted gateways for staking, governance, and web3. Whether it’s prime brokerage or international markets, we are building the scalable tech and seamless UI that empowers the biggest players on the planet to move money forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join us, and build the infrastructure for what’s next.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Software Engineer on the &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Foundations, Settlements and Transfers team&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, you will be at the core of Coinbase&#39;s financial infrastructure, ensuring the seamless and secure movement of funds. This team is responsible for processing transactions across fiat, crypto, and internal ledgers, and managing assets for our clients. You will lead the technical direction and mentorship for a team of engineers, playing a critical role in building and scaling the next generation of our financial systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement new financing products and features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and build new reporting, monitoring, tools, frameworks and APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with engineers, product managers and senior leadership to turn our vision into a tangible deliverables every quarter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improving developer efficiency, engineering excellence, and operational excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support to operations and other engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have at least 2+ years of experience in software engineering.&lt;br&gt;You’ve designed, built, scaled and maintained production services, and know how to compose a service oriented architecture.&lt;br&gt;You write high quality, well tested code to meet the needs of your customers.&lt;br&gt;You’re passionate about building an open financial system that brings the world together.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve worked with Golang, Ruby, Docker, Sinatra, Rails, Postgres, MongoDB or Redshift.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve built financial, high reliability or security systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have experience with Blockchains (such as Bitcoin, Ethereum, etc).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Job #: &lt;em&gt;P75989&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
