&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;SpaceX was founded under the belief that a future where humanity is out exploring the stars is fundamentally more exciting than one where we are not. Today SpaceX is actively developing the technologies to make this possible, with the ultimate goal of&amp;nbsp;enabling human life on Mars.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OPERATIONS DEVELOPMENT ENGINEER (STARLINK)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Starlink is the world’s largest satellite constellation and is providing fast, reliable internet to millions of users worldwide. We’ve only begun to scratch the surface of Starlink’s potential global impact and are looking for best-in-class engineers to help develop the systems that enable providing service in new markets and even greater system performance and growth potential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As an&amp;nbsp;Operations Development Engineer, you will&amp;nbsp;be responsible for&amp;nbsp;engineering&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;operational systems and processes used to support&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;Starlink&amp;nbsp;network as it scales to millions of users around the globe. Join the team&amp;nbsp;operating&amp;nbsp;the network that&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;revolutionizing global connectivity and&amp;nbsp;internet access.&amp;nbsp;A&amp;nbsp;successful&amp;nbsp;Operations Development Engineer&amp;nbsp;will create the tools, technology and processes to&amp;nbsp;maintain,&amp;nbsp;operate&amp;nbsp;and evolve the most advanced network in the solar system.&amp;nbsp;You will&amp;nbsp;utilize&amp;nbsp;operational data&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;identify&amp;nbsp;and prioritize various improvements that improve our operational efficiency and&amp;nbsp;maintain&amp;nbsp;the overall health of operations.&amp;nbsp;You will work with subsystem responsible engineers, software engineers,&amp;nbsp;and network engineers to develop alerts, mitigations,&amp;nbsp;and terrestrial assets and drive improvements to core Starlink systems.&amp;nbsp;Through continuous improvement, you will drive process and automation upgrades to the point of minimal manual intervention. You&amp;nbsp;will&amp;nbsp;be responsible for&amp;nbsp;the complete lifecycle of the projects&amp;nbsp;you&amp;nbsp;own, including development, testing,&amp;nbsp;deployment&amp;nbsp;and support.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;10&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Develop, implement and scale Starlink Network Operations processes and tools to provide global internet access&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Collect and analyze operations data to&amp;nbsp;identify&amp;nbsp;and implement&amp;nbsp;efficiency improvements for operational processes and workflows&amp;nbsp;and translate it into reporting, and recommendations for the development team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;10&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;3&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Collaborate with development teams to analyze the impact of proposed workflow or process changes on operations health and efficiency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Work with development engineering teams to drive design for operations,&amp;nbsp;identifying&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;addressing&amp;nbsp;potential&amp;nbsp;operational scaling issues early in development lifecycles&amp;nbsp;and incorporating debugging tools and strategies to&amp;nbsp;ensure effective handover to operations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Interact with key stakeholders to identify their desired outcomes, take their inputs and deliver improvements to Network Operations owned processes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Work with the diverse teams across the Starlink program to develop monitoring,&amp;nbsp;detection&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;response&amp;nbsp;processes&amp;nbsp;that&amp;nbsp;drive&amp;nbsp;quick&amp;nbsp;resolution to emergent&amp;nbsp;network events&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;10&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;7&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Define and develop projects, milestones, and&amp;nbsp;maintain&amp;nbsp;roadmaps, practicing flexible prioritization and scope management&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;deliver on program directives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Take extreme ownership of deliverables and make risk-conscious decisions under pressure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;10&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;9&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Own data integrity, tool &amp;amp; dashboard maintenance, and reporting quality for the Network Operations Engineering Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Define and develop department-level metrics and associated dashboards that quantify the health of our operations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
