&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Get to know Okta&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Okta is The World’s Identity Company. We free everyone to safely use any technology, anywhere, on any device or app. Our flexible and neutral products, Okta Platform and Auth0 Platform, provide secure access, authentication, and automation, placing identity at the core of business security and growth.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;At Okta, we celebrate a variety of perspectives and experiences. We are not looking for someone who checks every single box - we’re looking for lifelong learners and people who can make us better with their unique experiences.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Join our team! We’re building a world where Identity belongs to you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re hiring an Operations Specialist to own the backend operations—systems, measurement, and logistics—that keep the portfolio running for Auth0’s Strategic Programs and Communications team. This role is ideal for someone who enjoys operational work, takes pride in maintaining clean, reliable processes and systems, and is also excited to evolve how the team operates by leveraging AI thoughtfully. You’ll be expected to experiment with and use AI-enabled tools and automation, identify repeatable work that can be streamlined, and help deliver practical, AI-forward workflow improvements that increase speed and accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will act as the operational backbone for the team’s portfolio, responsible for all operational reporting and survey measurement across programs, maintaining the team’s core trackers and dashboards, and producing clear, leadership-ready presentations. You’ll also administer our program management tooling, oversee knowledge management (Confluence/Google Drive/Asana/Jira), drive procurement workflows, track onboarding completion, and manage Jira automations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The right candidate is energized by problem-solving, adaptable, communicates promptly and proactively, collaborates effectively across partners, navigates ambiguity with confidence, and continuously seeks opportunities to streamline work through process improvement, automation, and strategic AI usage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you’ll be doing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own &lt;strong&gt;portfolio operations&lt;/strong&gt; and routine backend work: maintain systems of record, build automations, keep trackers current, and ensure follow-through across deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own program &lt;strong&gt;measurement and reporting&lt;/strong&gt; end-to-end: build and maintain dashboards and trackers, run surveys and feedback cycles, analyze results, and deliver clear post-program readouts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify high-volume, repeatable workflows and deliver &lt;strong&gt;AI-enabled improvements &lt;/strong&gt;(including prompt and agent workflows, automation, and documentation) from pilot to rollout, with clear success measures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain &lt;strong&gt;hiring data&lt;/strong&gt; and related dashboards, providing regular insights and reporting with strong data integrity and clear status visibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own &lt;strong&gt;new hire onboarding operations&lt;/strong&gt;, including LMS administration, completion tracking and reporting, maintaining onboarding tooling and workflows, building and administering Jira automations, and driving continuous improvements as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer and improve the team’s work management practices, including portfolio hygiene, templates, and governance across tools such as Asana&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own &lt;strong&gt;knowledge management&lt;/strong&gt; across internal knowledge bases and shared drives: structure, taxonomy, audits, assets, and keeping information current and easy to find&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run and continuously improve &lt;strong&gt;procurement workflows&lt;/strong&gt;, including intake, approvals coordination, tracking, and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide &lt;strong&gt;event operations and logistics support&lt;/strong&gt; for key moments (virtual and in-person), including run-of-show management, registration workflow tooling, badge quality checks, audio-visual coordination, and on-site operational troubleshooting as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create &lt;strong&gt;visually polished&lt;/strong&gt; slides and reusable templates for reporting, operating updates, and quarterly program review support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify process gaps and implement &lt;strong&gt;improvements&lt;/strong&gt; using automation and AI, where it adds leverage and reduces manual work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel&lt;/strong&gt; ~15% of the time, including international, to support key programs and events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you bring to the role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in business, program, or enablement operations, with ownership of repeatable workflows and strong execution quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A high-detail, systems-oriented approach; you enjoy repetitive backend work and take pride in accuracy and follow-through&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong capability in &lt;strong&gt;data collection and reporting&lt;/strong&gt;, including survey-based measurement, data cleanup, analysis, and synthesis into clear insights. Tableau, Survey Monkey, and Qualtrics experience is a bonus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced &lt;strong&gt;Google Sheets&lt;/strong&gt; skills for dashboards and trackers; automation experience such as Apps Script, Zapier, or Make is a strong bonus&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable and fluent with &lt;strong&gt;AI tools,&lt;/strong&gt; including using AI-powered &lt;strong&gt;automation&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;agent-based workflows&lt;/strong&gt; to streamline workflows, reduce manual effort, and continuously improve operational processes, where appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to experiment, evaluate, and roll out new processes or AI-enabled workflows, including documenting changes and tracking impact (time saved, error reduction, adoption)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong &lt;strong&gt;Google Slides&lt;/strong&gt; design skills, including the ability to design clean, consistent, visually compelling decks and templates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with program management tools such as &lt;strong&gt;Asana&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Jira&lt;/strong&gt;, including maintaining standards and improving adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience owning or administering &lt;strong&gt;knowledge management&lt;/strong&gt;, including structure, governance, and content hygiene&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort supporting &lt;strong&gt;procurement workflows&lt;/strong&gt;, coordinating approvals, and maintaining accurate tracking and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication; prompt, proactive, and collaborative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated discretion and trust in handling sensitive and confidential information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong status management: you communicate progress, risks, and next steps clearly and consistently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to multitask and operate under pressure in a fast-paced, remote environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to navigate ambiguity, learn quickly, and take initiative with minimal oversight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bonus: &lt;strong&gt;Canva&lt;/strong&gt; and video editing experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be located in Chicago, IL, New York City, or Toronto, Canada&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#LI-REMOTE&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;#LI-SH1&lt;br&gt;P24801_3364397&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Below is the annual base salary range for candidates located in California (excluding San Francisco Bay Area), Colorado, Illinois, New York and Washington. Your actual base salary will depend on factors such as your skills, qualifications, experience, and work location. In addition, Okta offers equity (where applicable), bonus, and benefits, including health, dental and vision insurance, 401(k), flexible spending account, and paid leave (including PTO and parental leave) in accordance with our applicable plans and policies. To learn more about our Total Rewards program please visit:&lt;a href=&quot;https://rewards.okta.com/us&quot;&gt; https://rewards.okta.com/us&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;The annual base salary range for this position for candidates located in California (excluding San Francisco Bay Area), Colorado, Illinois, New York, and Washington is between:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$86,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$118,800 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;What you can look forward to as a Full-Time Okta employee!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Amazing &lt;a href=&quot;https://rewards.okta.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://rewards.okta.com/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1677948559087000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0Smv8KiGrXS3C1_LQmHF9D&quot;&gt;Benefits&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Making &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okta.com/okta-for-good/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.okta.com/okta-for-good/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1677948559087000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2kKFyZVPp9NLrjKMOBXtWi&quot;&gt;Social Impact&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okta.com/company/&quot;&gt;Talent and Fostering Connection + Community at Okta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Okta cultivates a dynamic work environment, providing the best tools, technology and benefits to empower our employees to work productively in a setting that best and uniquely suits their needs. Each organization is unique in the degree of flexibility and mobility in which they work so that all employees are enabled to be their most creative and successful versions of themselves, regardless of where they live. Find your place at Okta&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okta.com/company/careers/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.okta.com/company/careers/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1677948559087000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0Sy_6hHRhrwzwXgCfEiRV1&quot;&gt; today! &lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okta.com/company/careers/&quot;&gt;https://www.okta.com/company/careers/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Some roles may require travel to one of our office locations for in-person onboarding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Okta is an Equal Opportunity Employer. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, national origin, ancestry, marital status, age, physical or mental disability, or status as a protected veteran. We also consider for employment qualified applicants with arrest and convictions records, consistent with applicable laws. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If reasonable accommodation is needed to complete any part of the job application, interview process, or onboarding please use this&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1EfiEYZrIyhA2X4Fijk0R3RKYOzNoS3wtvyM4nhbZnXE/edit&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1EfiEYZrIyhA2X4Fijk0R3RKYOzNoS3wtvyM4nhbZnXE/edit&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1677948559087000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw152wP4kqe-oDJRAeGVJrN7&quot;&gt; Form&lt;/a&gt; to request an accommodation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Notice for New York City Applicants &amp;amp; Employees:&lt;/strong&gt; Okta may use Automated Employment Decision Tools (AEDT), as defined by New York City Local Law 144, that use artificial intelligence, machine learning, or other automated processes to assist in our recruitment and hiring process. In accordance with NYC Local Law 144, if you are an applicant or employee residing in New York City, please &lt;a href=&quot;https://talent.okta.com/new-york-city-aedt-notice.html&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;click here&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to view our full NYC AEDT Notice.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Okta is committed to complying with applicable data privacy and security laws and regulations. For more information, please see our Personnel and Job Candidate Privacy Notice at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okta.com/legal/personnel-policy/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.okta.com/legal/personnel-policy/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1759599734507000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3KZGmq4Ud_Aq6tycXCiDeT&quot;&gt;https://www.okta.com/legal/personnel-policy/.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Get to know Okta&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Okta is The World’s Identity Company. We free everyone to safely use any technology, anywhere, on any device or app. Our flexible and neutral products, Okta Platform and Auth0 Platform, provide secure access, authentication, and automation, placing identity at the core of business security and growth.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;At Okta, we celebrate a variety of perspectives and experiences. We are not looking for someone who checks every single box - we’re looking for lifelong learners and people who can make us better with their unique experiences.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Join our team! We’re building a world where Identity belongs to you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Washington, DC – Onsite 4 Days/Week (Mon–Thurs)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Relocation required if not local – no relocation assistance provided&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Okta, we’re building the world’s identity platform — one that empowers people, protects data, and fuels digital innovation. Our customers (think: JetBlue, T-Mobile, Sonos, Zoom) trust us to help them stay secure, seamless, and scalable in a world where everything and everyone is connected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And behind the tech? People like you — curious, motivated, collaborative learners who want to do meaningful work alongside great teammates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity: Where High Potential Meets High Impact&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let’s be real: There are a lot of SDR roles out there. But at Okta, we do things differently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn’t just a stepping stone — it’s your launchpad into a long-term sales career in one of the most exciting industries in tech: cybersecurity and identity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for driven, curious individuals who thrive in fast-paced environments, embrace feedback, and want to make a tangible impact every day. As an SDR at Okta, you&#39;ll do more than prospect — you’ll uncover real business challenges, collaborate cross-functionally, and set the foundation for meaningful customer relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research accounts and contacts to develop thoughtful outreach strategies using tools like Salesforce, Outreach, and LinkedIn Sales Navigator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Marketing and Account Executives to plan and execute prospecting campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage inbound leads and perform outbound outreach to generate high-quality meetings and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct discovery conversations to understand business needs and tee up your Account Executives for success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hit your call, email, meeting, and pipeline goals — and have fun doing it, with team competitions, shout-outs, and ongoing support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep your data organized and up-to-date in Salesforce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with cross-functional partners to continuously improve how we connect with our customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Makes You a Great Fit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree or equivalent work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6–12 months of prior business experience preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;strong communicator&lt;/strong&gt;, written and verbal — you know how to connect&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Self-motivated and goal-oriented&lt;/strong&gt; — you take initiative and follow through&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable managing priorities in a fast-paced, evolving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coachable&lt;/strong&gt; — you’re open to feedback and eager to grow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Curious&lt;/strong&gt; — you ask great questions and are always looking to learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with sales tools like Salesforce, Outreach, and Sales Navigator is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Few Logistics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This role is onsite in our Washington DC office 4 days per week (Mon–Thurs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If you&#39;re not already local, you’ll need to relocate within an agreed-upon timeframe — note that&amp;nbsp;Okta does not provide relocation assistance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll attend in-person onboarding in either San Francisco or Chicago to kick off your journey&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If you need a reasonable accommodation during the application or interview process,&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okta.com/company/careers/&quot;&gt; let us know here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Okta?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You could sell anything — so why not sell something that truly matters?&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Okta, we help people and businesses access the technology they need safely and easily. And behind our mission is a culture of trust, growth, and belonging. We invest in our people with real support, meaningful work, and the freedom to take ownership of your career from day one.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Join us, and you won’t just be starting a job — you’ll be joining a company that’s defining what’s next in identity, and building a safer digital world for everyone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
